'''一世代'''（{{lang-en|One Direction}}，簡稱{{lang|en|1D}}）是一个英国-爱尔兰男子音乐组合，成員包括[[奈爾·霍蘭|奈爾·霍蘭]]、[[連恩·佩恩|連恩·佩恩]]、[[哈利·斯泰爾斯|哈利·斯泰爾斯]]與[[路易·湯姆林森|路易·湯姆林森]]，2015年3月25日前[[贊恩·馬利克|贊恩·馬利克]]宣布退出該團體。組合成員在2010年參與[[英國版X音素|英國版X音素]]決賽取得第3名后與[[西蒙·高維爾|西蒙·高維爾]]的廠牌[[賽科音樂|賽科音樂]]簽約后正式出道。1世代還於[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会闭幕式|2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会闭幕式]]中表演。由於[[社交媒體|社交媒體]]的宣传，1世代迄今發行的五張專輯《[[青春無敵|青春無敵]]》、《[[青春滿屋|青春滿屋]]》、《[[青春午夜場|青春午夜場]]》、《[[青春第四課|青春第四課]]》和《[[青春創世紀|青春創世紀]]》都取得了一定的商業成功，并製造了《[[妳如此美麗|妳如此美麗]]》、《[[青春不留白|青春不留白]]》、《[[絕代好歌|絕代好歌]]》、《[[小事情_(1世代歌曲)|小事情]]》、《[[青春的故事|青春的故事]]》、《[[愛的勇士|愛的勇士]]》和《[[完美情人_(1世代歌曲)|完美情人]]》等熱門單曲。

自出道以來，1世代獲得了許多獎項，包括6個[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]、4個[[MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|MTV音樂錄影帶大獎]]、11個[[MTV歐洲音樂大獎|MTV歐洲音樂大獎]]、7個[[全美音樂獎|全美音樂獎]]、27個[[青少年選擇獎|青少年選擇獎]]與其它眾多獎項。除此以外，團體還被《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》評為2012年最佳新星。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1481395/one-direction-qas-with-billboards-top-new-artist-of-2012 |title=One Direction: Q&As With Billboard's Top New Artist of 2012 | first =Andrew | last = Hampp |work= [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher= [[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]] |date=2012-12-14 |accessdate=2012-12-14}}</ref>根據《[[星期日泰晤士報|星期日泰晤士報]]》財富榜2013年4月的報道，團體的估計身價約為2500萬英鎊，是英國第二富有的30歲以下藝人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sugarscape.com/main-topics/celebrities/851889/sunday-times-rich-list-2013-one-direction-zoom-under-30s-paul-mccartn|work=[[sugarscape.com|sugarscape.com]]|title=Sunday Times' rich list 2013, One direction, Zoom under 30, Paul McCartney|date=2013-04-10|accessdate=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110001856/http://www.sugarscape.com/main-topics/celebrities/851889/sunday-times-rich-list-2013-one-direction-zoom-under-30s-paul-mccartn|archive-date=2014-11-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2014年，《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》根據團體2013年6月到2014年6月期間賺得的7500萬美元將其列為30歲以下第二富有的名人。<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2848144/Justin-Bieber-Forbes-highest-earning-celebrity-30-pocketing-80m-year-just-cover-costly-legal-woes.html "Justin Bieber is Forbes' highest-earning celebrity under 30 pocketing $80m this year... which should just about cover his costly legal woes"]. Mail Online. Retrieved 25 November 2014</ref>2015年6月，《福布斯》根據團體前12個月1億3000萬美元的收入，<ref>[http://www.forbes.com/sites/maddieberg/2015/06/29/one-directions-earnings-130-million-in-2015/ "One Direction's Earnings: $130 Million in 2015"]. Forbes. Retrieved 4 November 2015</ref>將團體列為世界第4富有的名人<ref>{{cite news|title=The World's Highest-Paid Celebrities|url=http://www.forbes.com/celebrities/list/#tab:overall|agency=Forbes|date=2015-11-14}}</ref>。

在发行专辑《青春第四課》后，1世代成为了第一个四张专辑空降美国[[告示牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌二百强专辑榜]]冠军的团体。<ref>{{cite news|first=Keith|last=Caulfield|script-title=en:One Direction’s ‘Four’ Makes Historic No. 1 Debut on Billboard 200 Chart|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6327789/one-direction-four-no-1-debut-billboard-200|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2014-11-26 |accessdate=2014-11-26}}</ref>他们的第3张录音室专辑《青春午夜場》尽管发行于2013年年末，却成为了2013年全球销量最高的专辑。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-28599903 |title= One Direction top 2013 global album chart|work= BBC News|publisher=BBC |date= 2014-08-01|accessdate=2014-08-02}}</ref>团体的[[青春在哪里巡回演唱会|青春在哪里巡回演唱会]]是2014年票房最高的巡回演唱会之一，更是有史以来由团体举办的演唱会中票房最高的演唱会，票房达2820万美元<ref name="record tour">[http://www.therichest.com/expensive-lifestyle/money/top-10-highest-grossing-concert-tours-of-2014/ "Top 10 Highest-Grossing Concert Tours Of 2014"]. Richest.com. Retrieved 4 November 2015</ref>。2014年，《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》将1世代列为年度艺人<ref>{{cite news|last1=Caulfield|first1=Keith|title=Billboard's Artists of the Year: 1981-2014|url=http://www.billboard.com/photos/6415105/billboard-artist-of-the-year-gallery-1981-to-2014?i=540767|agency=Billboard|issue=23 June 2015|date=2015-01-13}}</ref><ref>[http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/year-in-music-2014/6386043/the-year-in-pop-2014-one-direction-frozen-pharrell "The Year in Pop 2014: One Direction, 'Frozen,' & Pharrell Dominate"]. Billboard. Retrieved 8 January 2015</ref>。2016年1月開始，团体在宣布休息後已暫時性的停止活動<ref>[http://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/music/800249/One-Direction-reunion-timing-Niall-Horan-solo-Harry-Styles One Direction REUNION: Niall Horan opens up on WHEN it will happen | Music | Entertainment | Express.co.uk<!-- 机器人生成的标题 -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.cnn.com/2017/02/15/celebrities/one-direction-reunion-niall-horan-interview/ One Direction reunion 'definitely' happening - CNN<!-- 擊倒我 -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4258530/Louis-Tomlinson-gushes-One-Direction-bandmates.html Louis Tomlinson gushes about his One Direction bandmates | Daily Mail Online<!-- 机器人生成的标题 -->]</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
===2010年–2011年：《X音素》===
[[File:One_Direction_X_Factor_Live_Glasgow.jpg|200px]]
2010年，[[奈爾·霍蘭|奈爾·霍蘭]]、[[贊恩·馬利克|贊恩·馬利克]]、[[連恩·佩恩|連恩·佩恩]]、[[哈利·斯泰爾斯|哈利·斯泰爾斯]]和[[路易·湯姆林森|路易·湯姆林森]]以个人身份参加了英国电视节目《[[英國版X音素|X音素]]》的第7季。<ref name=Kelly>{{cite news| first =Kristy | last = Kelly | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s103/the-x-factor/news/a331792/nicole-scherzinger-i-did-simon-cowell-a-favour-with-one-direction.html | title= Nicole Scherzinger: 'I did Simon Cowell a favour with One Direction' |work= [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]| publisher= Hearst | place = UK|date= 2011-07-26 | accessdate =2011-07-26}}</ref>但他们均未能成功晋级男子组評委之家。2010年7月，在节目中的训练营环节中，5人被安排成了一个组合继续参加比赛，<ref>{{cite news| first = Kate | last = McMahon| url = http://www.mirror.co.uk/celebs/news/2010/07/12/cheryl-tweedy-cancels-x-factor-boot-camp-and-v-festival-appearances-115875-22406276/ | title= Cheryl Tweedy cancels X Factor Boot Camp and V Festival appearances | work = The Daily Mirror |publisher= [[Trinity_Mirror|Trinity Mirror]]|date= 2010-07-12|accessdate= 2010-07-12}}</ref>并参加了组合组比赛。评委[[妮可·舒辛格|妮可·舒辛格]]<ref name=Kelly /><ref>{{cite news|title=One Direction film claims she founded band, not Simon Cowell|url=http://blogs.independent.co.uk/2013/07/19/more-woe-for-nicole-scherzinger-one-direction-film-claims-she-founded-band-not-simon-cowell/|newspaper=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|location=London|first=Daisy|last=Wyatt|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131122053550/http://blogs.independent.co.uk/2013/07/19/more-woe-for-nicole-scherzinger-one-direction-film-claims-she-founded-band-not-simon-cowell/|archivedate=2013-11-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Without Nicole Scherzinger there would be no One Direction |url=http://www.novafm.com.au/audio/without-nicole-scherzinger-there-would-be-no-one-direction |newspaper=NOVA Fm (Australian radio) |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401001002/http://www.novafm.com.au/audio/without-nicole-scherzinger-there-would-be-no-one-direction |archivedate=2012-04-01 }}</ref>和[[西蒙·高維爾|西蒙·高維爾]]均有让五人组成组合的想法。<ref name="1D Day">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a533467/simon-cowell-talks-one-direction-formation-it-was-my-idea.html|title=Simon Cowell talks One Direction formation: 'It was my idea'|last=Harp|first=Justin|date=2013-11-24|work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|publisher=[[赫斯特国际集团|Hearst Magazines UK]]|accessdate=2013-11-24}}</ref>接着，组合成员一起生活了2周去了解彼此并练习表演。<ref name="thehothits1">{{cite news|first1=Stan |last1=Walker |first2=Short |last2=Stack |first3=Michael |last3=Paynter |first4=Amy |last4=Meredith |url=http://www.thehothits.com/artists/6069/one-direction/bio |title=One Direction Biography |work=[[The_Hot_Hits_Live_from_LA|The Hot Hits Live from LA]] |publisher=MCM Media |accessdate=2012-04-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120327221234/http://www.thehothits.com/artists/6069/one-direction/bio |archivedate=2012-03-27 }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated10>{{cite web|newspaper=South Wales Echo |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/showbiz-and-lifestyle/showbiz/2012/01/13/one-direction-prepare-for-cardiff-sell-out-shows-91466-30112196/ |title=One Direction prepare for Cardiff sell-out shows |publisher=[[Media_Wales|Media Wales]] |date=2012-01-13 |accessdate=2012-06-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126001640/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/showbiz-and-lifestyle/showbiz/2012/01/13/one-direction-prepare-for-cardiff-sell-out-shows-91466-30112196/ |archivedate=2012-01-26 }}</ref>斯泰尔提出了组合名称“1世代”。<ref name="thehothits1" /> 在组合组评委之家晋级赛中，1世代清唱了Ednaswap乐团的歌曲《[[Torn_(Ednaswap歌曲)|Torn]]》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.stv.tv/tv/200816-the-x-factor-2010-the-acts-who-made-it-to-the-live-shows/ |work=[[蘇格蘭電視台|STV]] |place=[[蘇格蘭|SCO]], UK |title=The X Factor 2010: the 12 acts who made it to the Live Shows |date=2010-10-03 |accessdate=2011-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101124111354/http://entertainment.stv.tv/tv/200816-the-x-factor-2010-the-acts-who-made-it-to-the-live-shows/ |archivedate=2010-11-24 }}</ref>高維爾称他们的表演“自信、快乐，就像一群好友一般，丝毫不畏惧。”<ref name = "simoncowellQ&A">{{cite news| first = Andy | last = Greene |url = http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/exclusive-q-a-simon-cowell-on-one-directions-rise-to-stardom-20120409 |title=Exclusive Q&A: Simon Cowell on One Direction's Rise to Stardom |work=Rolling Stone |publisher=[[Jann_Wenner|Jann Wenner]] |date= 2012-04-09 |accessdate= 2012-05-11}}</ref>在表演后，团体在英国迅速获得名气。<ref name="simoncowellQ&A" />

1世代终在比赛中取得了第3名。而他们在决赛中演唱的歌曲《[[Forever_Young_(阿爾伐城歌曲)|Forever Young]]》也被发布于互联网上。<ref name = thirdplace>{{cite news|url= http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2010/dec/10/xfactor-final-results-liveblog |title=The X Factor 2010 final results show|work=The Guardian|date= 2012-12-12 |accessdate=2012-03-15 | location = London | first = Stuart | last = Heritage}}</ref>不久后，1世代确认与高維爾签下[[赛科唱片|赛科唱片]]200万的音乐合约。<ref>{{cite news | first = Lee | last = Cara | url = http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/tv/x_factor/3277896/Simon-Cowell-snaps-up-Cher-Rebecca-and-One-Direction.html |title=Father Xmas Si's three special gifts |work= The Sun | publisher = [[新聞集團英國|News International]] |date= 2010-12-15 |accessdate= 2012-01-04 |location= London}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Mayer | last = Nissim |url= http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/s103/the-x-factor/news/a300729/one-direction-get-gbp2m-syco-investment.html | title= One Direction 'get £2m Syco investment' | work= [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] | publisher = Hearst | place = UK | date=2011-01-28|accessdate=2011-10-23}}</ref>2011年1月，团体开始着手录制他们的第1张录音室专辑。<ref name = Miller>{{cite news | first = Ed | last = Miller |url = http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/sony-excited-about-one-direction-potential/046464 | title = Sony excited about One Direction potential |work= [[Music_Week|Music Week]] |publisher= Intent Media |date = 2011-08-16 | accessdate = 2012-07-27}}</ref>2月，团体出版了自己的第一本书籍《1世代：永遠年輕》，讲述了他们参加X音素比赛的经历。<ref>{{cite web| first =Alex | last = Fletcher | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/s103/the-x-factor/news/a304324/one-direction-release-autobiography.html | title= One Direction release autobiography |work= [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|publisher= Hearst | place = UK | date = 2011-02-17 | accessdate=2012-01-14}}</ref>这本书成功登上了[[星期日泰晤士報|《星期日泰晤士報》畅销书籍榜]]冠军。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.sugarscape.com/tags/band/621789/one-direction-number-one-sunday-times-bestseller-list?page=0%2C0 |title=One Direction book number one on Sunday Times bestsetller list |work= [[Sugar_(magazine)|Sugarscape]] |publisher= [[Hachette_Filipacchi_Médias|Hachette Filipacchi Médias]] |date= 2011-04-05|accessdate= 2012-07-27}}</ref>同月，团体与X音素其它参赛者一起开启了X音素2011年巡迴演唱會。<ref>{{cite news | first =Sophie | last = Freeman |title= Now Treyc Cohen snubbed by X Factor for £100,000 tour... but reject Aiden Grimshaw IS invited |url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1331129/X-Factor-2010-Treyc-Cohen-snubbed-Aiden-Grimshaw-stays-tour.html | work= The Daily Mail | publisher= [[Associated_Newspapers|Associated Newspapers]] | date= 2010-11-19 | accessdate = 2010-11-19 |location= London}}</ref>巡演在英国各地进行，共吸引了500,000观看人次 。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hmvtickets.com/events/1622?REFID=hmv_tickets_system_body |title=Tickets for One Direction at HMV Apollo Hammersmith, London, now available from hmvtickets.com |publisher=[[HMV|HMV]] |accessdate=2012-05-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121204017/http://www.hmvtickets.com/events/1622?REFID=hmv_tickets_system_body |archivedate=2012-01-21 }}</ref> 2011年4月，团体结束了巡演后开始继续制作专辑。<ref name="allmusic1">{{cite web | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/up-all-night-r2324993/credits |title= Up All Night – One Direction |work = AllMusic | publisher =[[Rovi_Corporation|Rovi Corporation]] |date=2011-11-21 |accessdate=2012-03-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media notes | title =Up All Night |others=One Direction |date=2011 |type=liner notes |publisher= [[赛科音乐|Syco Music]], [[索尼音樂娛樂|Sony Music Entertainment]]}}</ref>

