2011年9月，1世代发行了他们的首张单曲《[[妳如此美麗|妳如此美麗]]》。單曲是[[索尼音樂|索尼音樂]]史上預購成績最佳的單曲，并在[[英國單曲榜|英國單曲榜]]獲得了冠軍。<ref>{{cite news | first =Lewis | last = Corner |url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a335956/one-directions-what-makes-you-beautiful-breaks-pre-order-sales-record.html | title=One Direction's 'What Makes You Beautiful' breaks pre-order sales record |work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|publisher=Hearst | place = UK|date=2011-08-19|accessdate=2011-08-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Alan | last = Jones | url = http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=22&storycode=1046622 | title = What Makes You Beautiful becomes fastest seller of the year | work= [[Music_Week|Music Week]] | publisher = Intent Media |date = 2011-09-19 |accessdate= 2012-01-05}}</ref>隨後，團體發佈的單曲《[[非妳莫屬_(1世代歌曲)|非妳莫屬]]》和《[[神奇的魔力|神奇的魔力]]》都進入了英國單曲榜單前10名。 <ref>{{cite news| first = Alan | last = Jones |url= http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1047553&c=1 |title=UK Singles Chart Analysis: Rihanna equals Adele record |work=[[Music_Week|Music Week]] |publisher = Intent Media|date=2011-11-21 |accessdate=2012-06-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| first =Alan | last = Jones |url = http://www.musicweek.com/story.asp?sectioncode=1&storycode=1048551&c=1 |title = Official Chart Analysis: Emeli Sande album sells 113k, DJ Fresh single shifts 128k |work= [[Music_Week|Music Week]] |publisher=Intent Media |date=2012-02-20 | accessdate = 2012-03-17}}</ref>2011年11月，團體在北美與[[哥倫比亞唱片|哥倫比亞唱片]]簽約。<ref>{{cite web| first = Lewis | last = Corner| url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a352201/one-direction-sign-us-record-deal-with-adele-label-columbia.html |title=One Direction sign U.S. record deal with Adele label Columbia | work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|publisher= Hearst | place = UK |date= 2011-11-22 |accessdate= 2012-01-14}}</ref>2012年2月，《妳如此美麗》在美國發行。<ref>{{cite news| first =Amanda | last = Hasaka |url= http://www.celebuzz.com/2012-02-14/one-directions-debut-single-what-makes-you-beautiful-now-available-on-itunes/ |title=One Direction's Debut Single 'What Makes You Beautiful' Now Available On iTunes! |work= Celebuzz |publisher=[[Buzz_Media|Buzz Media]]|date=2012-02-14 |accessdate= 2012-02-15}}</ref>歌曲空降[[告示牌百強單曲榜|《告示牌》百強單曲榜]]第28名，成為英國藝人1998年來最高空降。<ref name="Hot100">{{cite web |url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/504475/one-direction-has-highest-hot-100-debut-for-new-uk-act-since-1998 |title= One Direction Has Highest Hot 100 Debut For New UK Act Since 1998 |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |publisher= [[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]] |date= 2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-03-13}}</ref>歌曲在美國獲得了超過400萬份銷量。<ref name="sales2013">{{cite news |url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-jan-27-2013-songs-another-f-233455441.html |title= Week Ending Jan. 27, 2013. Songs: Another F**kin' Top 10 Hit | first =Paul | last = Grein|work=[[Yahoo!_Music|Music]] | publisher = [[雅虎|Yahoo!]] |date=2013-01-30 |accessdate= 2013-01-30}}</ref>為打開北美市場，1世代於2012年2月抵達美國進行宣傳。并作為[[派對男孩|派對男孩]]的[[與你更好巡迴演唱會|與你更好巡迴演唱會]]的暖場嘉賓隨派對男孩一起在北美演出。<ref>{{cite news| first =Mark | last = Savage|url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-18083174 |title= The U.S. love affair with British pop|work= News |publisher= BBC|date= 2010-05-21 | accessdate=2010-07-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| first =Stephan | last = Lee|url= http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/02/03/one-direction-big-time-rush-exclusive-photo/ | title= Exclusive Photo: One Direction and Big Time Rush unite for North American tour!|work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|publisher=[[时代公司|Time]] |accessdate= 2012-02-04}}</ref>1世代的第1張錄音室專輯《[[青春無敵|青春無敵]]》於2012年年初全球發行，在16個國家的專輯榜單獲得了冠軍。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/one-direction-to-hold-global-twitter-viewing-party-for-new-concert-dvd/049052 | title = One Direction to hold global Twitter viewing party for new concert DVD | work= [[Music_Week|Music Week]] | publisher = Intent Media | date=2012-05-30 |accessdate= 2012-06-11}}</ref>其中，因專輯在美國[[告示牌二百強專輯榜|《告示牌》二百強專輯榜]]奪冠，1世代成為第一個出道專輯即在美國獲得冠軍的英國團體。<ref>{{cite news| first =Keith | last = Caulfield | title = One Direction Makes History With No. 1 Debut on Billboard 200|url= http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/499420/one-direction-makes-history-with-no-1-debut-on-billboard-200 |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |publisher = [[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]] | date = 2012-03-20 | accessdate= 2012-03-21}}</ref>1世代也因此被寫入了《[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]》。<ref>{{cite news| first = Colin | last = Daniels| url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a404538/adele-one-direction-enter-guinness-world-records.html |title=Adele, One Direction enter 'Guinness World Records' | work = [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] |publisher=Hearst | place = UK |date=2012-09-07 | accessdate =2012-09-08}}</ref>截至2012年8月，專輯在全球已獲得超過300萬份銷量。<ref name = "Yahoosales">{{cite news | title = Week Ending Oct. 21, 2012. Albums: Aldean's Fast Train To #1 | url = http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-oct-21-2012-albums-aldean-fast-150305200.html | first =Paul | last = Grein |work= Music |publisher = Yahoo! |date= 2012-10-24 | accessdate = 2012-10-24|location= [[美国|U.S.]]}}</ref><ref name = "12millionsales">{{cite web| first =Dan | last = Lane|url = http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/one-direction-sell-12-million-singles-albums-and-dvd-and-blu-rays-worldwide-1516/ |title = One Direction sell 12 million singles, albums and DVD and Blu-rays worldwide | publisher = [[官方榜单公司|Official Charts Company]] |date=2012-08-02 |accessdate=2012-08-02}}</ref>

