= 2012-04-08|archiveurl= http://www.freezepage.com/1333939933IFYQZGQCXW | archivedate= 2012-04-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| last =Brandle | first = Lars|title= One Direction Live: Shriek Show in Australia | url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/photos/live/492534/one-direction-live-shriek-show-in-australia| work = [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate= 2012-07-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| first1 =Cameron | last1 = Adams | last2 = Siobhan | first2 = Duck|url = http://www.heraldsun.com.au/entertainment/music/one-directions-melbourne-concert-sells-out-in-three-minutes/story-e6frf9hf-1226286954743 |title=One Direction's Melbourne concert sells out in three minutes|work=Herald Sun |location= [[澳大利亚|AU]] |publisher= [[The_Herald_and_Weekly_Times|The Herald and Weekly Times]]|date= 2012-03-02|accessdate=2012-07-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first =Bridget | last = Jones|url= http://www.stuff.co.nz/auckland/whats-on/6512032/One-Directions-NZ-tour-sold-out |title=One Direction's NZ tour sold out|work= [[Stuff.co.nz|Stuff]] | place = [[新西兰|NZ]] | publisher = [[Fairfax_Media|Fairfax Media]] | date = 2012-03-02| accessdate= 2012-07-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| first = Emily | last = Hewett |url = http://www.metro.co.uk/music/877239-one-direction-tickets-fans-bombard-ticketmaster-as-ebay-touts-capitalise |title= One Direction tickets: Fans bombard Ticketmaster as eBay touts capitalise| work = [[Metro_(British_newspaper)|Metro]]|publisher= [[Associated_Newspapers|Associated Newspapers]]| date= 2011-10-01| accessdate= 2012-07-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title= One Direction to Headline Madison Square Garden December 3, 2012 |url = http://www.kait8.com/story/17325179/one-direction-to-headline-madison-square-garden-december-3-2012 |work= [[KAIT|KAIT]] | publisher = [[Raycom_Media|Raycom Media]] |date=2012-04-03 |accessdate=2012-04-08|archiveurl= http://www.freezepage.com/1333943764HSQQZOQYGS | archivedate = 2012-04-08}}</ref>巡演的DVD《[[青春無敵：尖叫演唱會|青春無敵：尖叫演唱會]]》於2012年5月發佈。<ref name="musicDVD">{{cite news | first = Lewis | last = Corner |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a376053/one-direction-perform-moments-on-tour-video.html |title = One Direction perform 'Moments' on tour | type = video | work= [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] | publisher= Hearst | place = UK |date = 2012-04-12 |accessdate= 2012-04-27}}</ref>DVD在25國奪冠，截至2012年8月已在全球獲得了超過100萬份銷量。<ref name="12millionsales"/><ref name =DVDWW>{{cite news | first =Rhian | last = Jones |url= http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/one-direction-live-dvd-hits-no1-in-25-countries/049138 | title= One Direction live DVD hits No.1 in 25 countries | work= [[Music_Week|Music Week]] | publisher = Intent Media | date = 2012-06-08 |accessdate=2012-06-11}}</ref>2012年5月，1世代在北美出版了自己的第一本書籍《敢於夢想：像「1世代」這樣活著》，獲得了[[紐約時報暢銷書榜|《紐約時報》暢銷書榜]]冠軍。<ref>{{cite news| url= http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2012-06-10/paperback-books/list.html |work=The New York Times | title=Best Sellers | date=2012-06-10 | accessdate = 2012-08-24 | first=Gregory | last=Cowles}}</ref>2012年8月，團體在[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会闭幕式|2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会闭幕式]]上表演。<ref name="12millionsales"/><ref>{{cite news | first =Kia | last = Makarechi |url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/08/12/one-direction-closing-ceremony-olympics_n_1770803.html |title= One Direction & Closing Ceremony: Olympics Get A Dose Of 'What Makes You Beautiful' | work = [[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]]| date= 2012-08-12 |accessdate=2012-08-13}}</ref>2012年9月6日，1世代在[[2012年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2012年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]獲得了3個獎項，包括最佳新人獎，成為了當晚最大贏家。<ref name= videomusicawards>{{cite news| place = UK | first =Amelia | last = Butterfly |url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/19515754 | title= One Direction win three MTV Video Music Awards in LA | work = Newsbeat | publisher = BBC|date=2012-09-07|accessdate=2012-09-07}}</ref>

