1世代於2012年5月開始在斯德哥爾摩的Kinglet錄音室錄製他們的第2張錄音室專輯。<ref name=credits>{{cite AV media notes |title = Take Me Home |others=One Direction |date=2012 |type=liner notes |publisher=[[赛科音乐|Syco Records]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/one-direction/354656-one-direction-sweden |title= One Direction Recording Second Album |work=MTV News |publisher=Viacom|date=2012-05-11 |accessdate=2012-08-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/one-direction/news/new-album/ |title= One Direction Enjoy "Amazing Day" In The Studio Recording New Album |publisher=Capital (Global Radio)|date=2012-05-12 |accessdate=2012-08-25}}</ref>專輯的首張單曲，《[[青春不留白|青春不留白]]》於2012年9月發佈。歌曲在幾乎所有國家進入了前10名，并創下了非美國藝人在美國最高單週單曲銷量紀錄。<ref>{{cite news| first =Tina| last = Hart|url = http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/one-direction-have-fastest-selling-single-by-a-uk-artist/052114 | title = One Direction achieve fastest-selling single by a UK act in the U.S. |work= Music Week |publisher= Intent Media|date= 2012-10-21 |accessdate=2012-10-11|location=United Kingdom}}</ref>2012年11月，專輯的第2支單曲《[[小事情_(1世代歌曲)|小事情]]》發佈。同月，團體的第2張錄音室專輯《[[青春滿屋|青春滿屋]]》正式發行。<ref name="TMH">{{cite web|url= https://itunes.apple.com/nl/album/take-me-home/id572141438|title= Take Me Home | work =[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] |publisher=[[蘋果公司|Apple]] |accessdate=2012-11-16|language=nl| location = Netherlands}}</ref>《青春滿屋》和《小事情》一起空降了英國專輯榜和單曲榜冠軍。<ref>{{cite news | first = Alan | last = Jones | url = http://www.musicweek.com/businessanalysis/read/official-charts-analysis-one-direction-youngest-ever-act-to-hit-no-1-in-albums-and-singles-lists/052592 |title=Official Charts Analysis: One Direction youngest ever act to score No. 1 Album and Single simultaneously |work=[[Music_Week|Music Week]] |publisher=Intent Media|date=2012-11-19 |accessdate=2012-11-19| location = [[英国|UK]]}}</ref>《青春滿屋》在美國獲得了540,000份首週銷量，空降《告示牌》二百強專輯榜冠軍。<ref name = "USTMHdebut">{{cite web|url= http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474059/one-directions-take-me-home-debuts-at-no-1-with-years-third-biggest-opening |title=One Direction's 'Take Me Home' Debuts at No. 1 With Year's Third-Biggest Opening | work=Billboard |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2012-11-20|accessdate= 2012-11-22 | location = [[美国|U.S.]]}}</ref>在全球來看，專輯在超過34國奪冠。<ref>{{cite news| first =Tina | last = Hart|url = http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/imagem-music-signs-one-direction-hit-writer-fiona-bevan/052709 |title=Imagem Music signs One Direction hit-writer Fiona Bevan |work=[[Music_Week|Music Week]] |publisher=Intent Media|date=2012-11-29 | accessdate =2012-12-01|location= [[英国|UK]]}}</ref>整個2012年，《青春無敵》和《青春滿屋》各自分別以超過500萬份銷量排行該年全球專輯銷售榜單的第3與第4。<ref name="Modest Management">{{cite web|url=http://www.modestmanagement.com/one-direction/ |title=One Direction |publisher=Modest Management |date= |accessdate=2014-08-02}}</ref>

2012年11月，1世代在[[皇家大匯演|皇家大匯演]]中表演，[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]觀看了他們的演出。<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/queen-elizabeth-II/9690193/Royal-Variety-Performance-2012-One-Direction-and-Girls-Aloud-sing-for-The-Queen.html |title=Royal Variety Performance 2012: One Direction and Girls Aloud sing for The Queen |work=[[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]]| date= 2012-11-20 | accessdate = 2012-11-24 |location=London}}</ref>12月，團體在紐約[[麦迪逊广场花园|麦迪逊广场花园]]演出，門票售罄。<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.billboard.com/articles/photos/live/473866/one-direction-headlines-sold-out-show-at-madison-square-garden |title=One Direction Headlines Sold-Out Show at Madison Square Garden|date=2012-12-04| accessdate =2012-12-05|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media| first =Andrew | last = Hampp}}</ref>2013年2月，1世代為[[喜劇救濟|喜劇救濟]]活動發佈了單曲《[[愛的方式|愛的方式]]》。作為1世代參與英國慈善的一部分，團體前往了[[加納|加納]]去兒童醫院當志願者，拜訪學校，進行募捐。<ref name="Robertson">{{cite news|url= http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/one-direction-reflect-on-life-changing-1535079 |title='We are the most selfish people ever': One Direction reflect on 'life changing' charity trip to Africa 'slums'|date=2013-01-15|accessdate=2013-02-16 | work =Metro| first =James | last = Robertson}}</ref>同月，1世代開啟了他們的第2個巡迴演唱會[[青春滿屋巡迴演唱會|青春滿屋巡迴演唱會]]。<ref>{{cite news| first =Jocelyn | last = Vena|url= http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1682975/one-direction-tour-dates.jhtml | title= One Direction Announce U.S. Dates On 2013 World Tour | work = News |publisher=MTV |date=2012-04-12 |accessdate=2012-04-20}}</ref>巡演宣佈舉辦當日就有300,000份門票售出。<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/one-direction/349694-one-direction-tickets |title=One Direction Fans in Ticket-Buying Frenzy |work=[[MTV_News|News]] | publisher =[[維亞康姆傳媒電視網|MTV]] |date=2012-02-26 |accessdate=2012-04-20}}</ref>巡演取得了一定的商業成功，在全球共進行了超過134場演出，總共售出了門票1,635,000張。<ref name="Box Office">{{cite web|url=http://onedirectionmusic.com/ |title=One Direction | Welcome to the One Direction website! |publisher=Onedirectionmusic.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-02}}</ref>

