romote-new-single-Story-My-Life.html|title=Breaking hearts from the get go: One Direction share adorable childhood photos to promote new single Story of My Life|work=Daily Mail|date=2013-10-11|first=Joanna|last=Crawley|location=London}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.celebuzz.com/2013-10-10/one-direction-announces-story-of-my-life-single-through-baby-photos/|title=One Direction Announces 'Story of My Life' Single Through Baby Photos|work=Celebuzz|date=2013-10-11|last=Chung|first=Gabrielle}}</ref>2013年11月23日，团体参与了1世代日活动，在线上与粉丝互动。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1dday.com/ |title=Welcome to 1D Day – 1D Day – One Direction |publisher=1dday.com |date=2013-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213102853/http://www.1dday.com/gb/home | archive-date= 2013-12-13 | accessdate=2014-01-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a533434/one-direction-1d-day-live-stream-watch.html |title=One Direction '1D Day' Live Stream - watch - Showbiz News |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2013-11-23 |accessdate=2014-01-19}}</ref>

團體的第3張錄音室專輯《[[青春午夜場|青春午夜場]]》於2013年11月25日發行。專輯在英美二國均空降冠軍。至此，1世代成為第1個前3張專輯都空降《告示牌》二百強專輯榜的團體。<ref name="Billboard record">{{cite news|first=Keith|last=Caulfield|title=One Direction Scores Historic Third No. 1 Album on Billboard 200 Chart|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5812384/one-direction-scores-historic-third-no-1-album-on-billboard-200-chart|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2013-12-04|accessdate=2013-12-04}}</ref>为宣传专辑，1世代在《X音素》[[X音素_(美国真人秀)|美国版]]和[[英国版X音素|英国版]]进行了宣传演出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heatworld.com/Celeb-News/2013/10/One-Direction-confirmed-for-The-X-Factor/|title=One Direction confirmed for The X Factor 2013 live shows|work=heatworld.com|last=Lewis|first=Anna|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018011227/http://www.heatworld.com/Celeb-News/2013/10/One-Direction-confirmed-for-The-X-Factor/|archivedate=2013-10-18}}</ref>

