hor=Abbey, Lewis | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329001801/http://www.inveterate.co.uk/music/one-direction-zayn-malik-confirms-departure-from-band/145871 | archivedate=2015-03-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Zayn Malik officially quits One Direction|url=http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2015/03/25/zayn-malik-leaves-one-direction/|website=[[福斯新聞頻道|Fox News]]|accessdate=2015-03-25|date=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325193633/http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2015/03/25/zayn-malik-leaves-one-direction/|archive-date=2015-03-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Lynch|first1=Joe|title=Zayn Malik Explains One Direction Exit: 'I Have To Do What Feels Right in My Heart'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6509661/zayn-malik-one-direction-exit-explanation|accessdate=2015-03-25|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|agency=[[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2015-03-25|location=United States}}</ref>5月14日，1世代第一次以四人團體公開露面，並稱不會再讓新的第5人加入1世代。<ref>[http://www.people.com/article/one-direction-interview-zayn-malik-james-corden-late-late-show One Direction Discusses Zayn Malik's Departure with James Corden: We Were a Little Bit Angry - One Direction, The Late Late Show with James Corden, Music News, TV News, Harry ...<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>巡演於2015年10月31日在英國[[谢菲尔德|谢菲尔德]]結束。<ref name="Sony Music Entertainment"/>

=== 2015年–2016年：《青春創世紀 (Made In The A.M.)》與暫時休團 ===
2015年7月31日，團體在毫無宣傳的情況下發佈了單曲《[[愛的勇士|愛的勇士]]》。這首歌曲是馬利克離團後1世代發佈的第1首歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|title=One Direction Shares First Track Without Zayn Malik, 'Drag Me Down'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6649246/one-direction-shares-first-track-without-zayn-malik-drag-me-down|website=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2015-07-31|date=2015-07-31}}</ref>11月13日，團體的第5張錄音室專輯《[[青春創世紀|青春創世紀]]》正式發佈。<ref>[http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6706833/one-direction-justin-bieber-album-release-november-13-poll "One Direction & Justin Bieber Album Release Showdown Set for November 13?"]. Billboard. Retrieved 25 October 2015</ref>專輯空降英國專輯榜冠軍。而在美國則以402,000份首週銷量空降亞軍，此首週銷量超過了團體上一張專輯《青春第四課》的銷量。<ref>{{cite web|title = Does One Direction's 'Midnight Memories' Follow The Boy Band Third-Album Trend? {{!}} Billboard|url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5800882/does-one-directions-midnight-memories-follow-the-boy-band-third|website = Billboard|accessdate = 2015-12-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title = Sorry, boy band haters: One Direction seems unstoppable|url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2014/11/18/sorry-boy-band-haters-one-direction-seems-unstoppable/|newspaper = The Washington Post|date = 2014-11-18|access-date = 2015-12-15|issn = 0190-8286|first = Emily|last = Yahr}}</ref>不久后，團體成員路易·湯姆林森宣佈團體將開始一個大約18個月的休假。而2015年12月31日晚團體在《[[迪克·克拉克的跨年搖滾夜|迪克·克拉克的跨年搖滾夜]]》上的表演也成為團體休假前最後一場公開演出。<ref name=thewrap-1d2016>{{cite web|script-title=en:One Direction Returns to Headline ‘Dick Clark’s New Year’s Rockin’ Eve’ Billboard Party|url=https://www.thewrap.com/one-direction-returns-to-headline-dick-clarks-new-years-rockin-eve-billboard-party/|website=TheWrap|accessdate=2015-11-24|date=2015-11-18}}</ref>

2016年1月，《[[我們周刊|我們周刊]]》報道稱團體4名成員在[[青春再前進巡迴演唱會|青春再前進巡迴演唱會]]后均未以團體的名義續約廠牌。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Blynn|first1=Jamie|title=One Direction Is Splitting, Extended Hiatus to Become a Permanent Break|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/one-direction-is-splitting-hiatus-to-become-a-permanent-break-w161510|accessdate=2016-01-13|work={{tsl|en|Us Weekly||Us Weekly}}|agency={{tsl|en|Jann Wenner||Wenner Media}} [[有限公司|LLC]]|date=2016-01-13|location=United States}}</ref>2月，已證實斯泰爾已脫離團體的管理，或開啟個人職業生涯。<ref>{{cite web|author=Marc Schneider |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/6859541/harry-styles-management-jeffrey-azoff-modest |title=Harry Styles Splits With One Direction's Management, Joins Azoff |publisher=Billboard |date= |accessdate=2016-09-09}}</ref>6月，斯泰爾已以個人身份與廠牌簽約。<ref>{{cite web|author=Shirley Halperin |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7416429/harry-styles-solo-record-deal-one-direction |title=Harry Styles Signs a Solo Record Deal With Columbia: Exclusive |publisher=Billboard |date=2016-06-23 |accessdate=2016-09-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.australianetworknews.com/one-direction-harry-styles-solo-albums/ |title=One Direction Split? Harry Styles 3 Solo Albums In the Works! - Aussie Network News |website=Australianetworknews.com |date=2016-07-01 |accessdate=2016-09-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Taylor Weatherby |url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2016/06/30/harry-styles-record-deal-80-million-contract-solo-albums-how-many/ |title=Harry Styles Record Deal Worth $80 Million — How Many Albums Will He Be Making? |publisher=Hollywood Life |date=2016-06-30 |accessdate=2016-09-09}}</ref>7月，佩恩稱已以個人身份與[[國會音樂集團|國會音樂集團]]簽約。<ref>{{cite web|last=Melas |first=Chloe |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/21/entertainment/liam-payne-signs-record-deal-one-direction/ |title=Liam Payne signs record deal. Leaving One Direction? |website=CNN.com |date=2016-07-21 |accessdate=2016-09-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Mitchell Peters |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7446504/one-direction-liam-payne-announces-solo-deal-with-capitol-records-uk |title=One Direction's Liam Payne Announces Solo Deal With Capitol Records UK |publisher=Billboard |date=2016-07-21 |accessdate=2016-09-09}}</ref>而截至2017年5月，团体的全部成员均已发布了个人单曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7808577/one-direction-solo-singles-ranked-list|title=Every One Direction Solo Single, Ranked|work=Billboard|date=2017-05-25|first=Andrew|last=Unterberger}}</ref>

